{"tid":1417403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個屯門友 經過今晚我想講......","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:17:44.000Z","uid":191784,"like":45,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f8edda5e300f2eedd3192f20db2e30574b51f559","tid":1417403,"uid":191784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"物資鏈都唔識得排 得幾個手足同我自己搬嘢<br />\n前線經常性互屌 為on9原則爭執<br />\n推前防線淨set一邊 勸左幾次先有人同我推埋另一邊<br />\n淨係瘋狂掟狗屋玻璃 同放幾次火辛苦隔離消防<br />\n前線好冇經驗 哨兵放風極唔準<br />\n太多花生友打咭友 一大班mk仔mk妹 背心短裙得個口罩可以同我企到最前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上都係前線既事實 同為屯門友既我係好灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我依然會繼續撐屯門 因為呢個係我從小長大既地方<br />\n<br />\n大家其實做得好好 be water級數有可能係全港第一（你可以話我地淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）完全達至不被捕<br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好再分化 兼不斷進化 細佬妹請唔好貪靚上齊裝先行前 得閒禮拜六日出黎發多啲夢<br />\n要做前線多睇戰術po 了解多啲前線係要做乜嘢 你放錯風手騰腳震對成個活動好大影響 幾千人係你後面以我地馬首是瞻<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後 我愛屯門 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"9fa04ef061281c563968031a502c2d10a75a6305","tid":1417403,"uid":15011,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:44:23.000Z","msg":"發夢喺屯門前線<br />\n真心想講 預咗畀人屌分化<br />\n<br />\n頭先大家明明傾咗一齊走<br />\n跟住啲人想撤嘅時候又有人唔郁 跟住屌人走<br />\n仲要態度極差 極差 極差<br />\n懇請各位巴打 如果真係唔想走<br />\n麻煩討論個陣就提出<br />\n唔好完咗先喺屌人<br />\n咁樣好黑人憎<br />\n<br />\n仲有 有一個冇gear 口罩都冇嘅人突然出現<br />\n話佢啱啱到 叫大家唔好走<br />\n但到頭來 大家去晒前個陣佢又唔見咗<br />\n仲要喺到話自己食過好多催淚彈<br />\n又話革命要犧牲<br />\n咁點解大家去前個陣佢又要企後面<br />\n要留可以 唔好講一套做一套<br />\n<br />\n發洩完畢<br />\n之後嘅發夢都會keep住去<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"37fb9ec3c4ed25a03aa93a9413115a24a75a1559","tid":1417403,"uid":67816,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce217c8d542fde3f4370f1417a758f196f94c23","tid":1417403,"uid":191784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"個夢太真實 抽離唔到"},{"pid":"28af1c0f87bbd3e5db5ac99f24677e66dd106a27","tid":1417403,"uid":191784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"37fb9ec3c4ed25a03aa93a9413115a24a75a1559","tid":1417403,"uid":67816,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:49:34.000Z","msg":"真 好多人完全唔記得左咩叫各有各做"},{"pid":"42af5bdb8def5d09bfde217eb91ca7b80e588607","tid":1417403,"uid":212973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb4ffb74a117c37e0cf8121bd9c39d1075dfa5d","tid":1417403,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:50:31.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"092176868bf44f543e5e491ae14953627be51e23","tid":1417403,"uid":53806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"屯門朋友睇完post要實戰架<br />\n快啲學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：屯門友"},{"pid":"7eca8091b557b80169e1bb26ba4264fe8068df50","tid":1417403,"uid":264578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:54:14.000Z","msg":"去到都諗緊點解冇物資鏈"},{"pid":"27b1b551e8ff22ad75a2537ef01a6e8d130e5c83","tid":1417403,"uid":46966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />岩嫁啦食多幾發啦<br />\n天水圍前幾日都係咁"},{"pid":"60a77b356223876081a6880426b80f90819dcf3f","tid":1417403,"uid":238301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:57:42.000Z","msg":"仲要唔封巴士總站個位<br />\n係